statements: SELECT * FROM bioenergy_research_data LIMIT 5;
SELECT biofuel_type, efficiency FROM bioenergy_research_data WHERE efficiency > 0.7;
SELECT biofuel_type, conversion_technique FROM bioenergy_research_data WHERE biofuel_type = 'Biomass';
SELECT * FROM bioenergy_research_data WHERE conversion_technique LIKE '%Pyrolysis%';
SELECT experiment_id, biofuel_type, efficiency FROM bioenergy_research_data ORDER BY efficiency DESC;
SELECT * FROM bioenergy_research_data WHERE efficiency > 0.75 ORDER BY biofuel_type ASC, conversion_technique DESC
SELECT experiment_id, biofuel_type, efficiency FROM bioenergy_research_data WHERE biofuel_type = 'Biodiesel'
SELECT experiment_id, efficiency FROM bioenergy_research_data WHERE efficiency BETWEEN 0.6 AND 0.8 ORDER BY efficiency DESC
SELECT biofuel_type, AVG(efficiency) AS average_efficiency FROM bioenergy_research_data GROUP BY biofuel_type HAVING AVG(efficiency) > 0.7
SELECT * FROM bioenergy_research_data ORDER BY efficiency DESC, biofuel_type ASC
SELECT * FROM Biofuel_Conversion_Research;
SELECT research_title, researcher_name FROM Biofuel_Conversion_Research;
SELECT researcher_name, research_date FROM Biofuel_Conversion_Research WHERE research_id = 1;

SELECT research_title, conversion_efficiency, biofuel_type FROM Biofuel_Conversion_Research JOIN Biofuel_Efficiency_Data ON Biofuel_Conversion_Research.research_id = Biofuel_Efficiency_Data.research_id;
SELECT * FROM Biofuel_Efficiency_Data WHERE biofuel_type = 'Biodiesel';
SELECT * FROM Biofuel_Conversion_Research WHERE research_id = 1;
SELECT research_title, researcher_name FROM Biofuel_Conversion_Research ORDER BY research_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM Biofuel_Efficiency_Data WHERE biofuel_type = 'Biodiesel' ORDER BY conversion_efficiency DESC;
SELECT research_id, biofuel_type, conversion_efficiency FROM Biofuel_Efficiency_Data WHERE conversion_efficiency >= 0.8;
SELECT researcher_name, research_date FROM Biofuel_Conversion_Research WHERE research_date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2021-01-01';
SELECT * FROM biofuel_experiments;
SELECT experiment_date, biofuel_type FROM biofuel_experiments WHERE conversion_efficiency > 0.8;
SELECT experiment_id, biofuel_type, conversion_efficiency FROM biofuel_experiments WHERE biofuel_type = 'Biodiesel';
SELECT * FROM experimental_conditions ORDER BY temperature DESC, pressure ASC;
SELECT team_id, researcher_name, institution, email FROM research_team WHERE institution = 'University of Science';
SELECT * FROM biofuel_experiments WHERE conversion_efficiency > 0.8 ORDER BY experiment_date;
SELECT experiment_date, biofuel_type FROM biofuel_experiments WHERE biofuel_type = 'Biodiesel';
SELECT experiment_id, conversion_efficiency FROM biofuel_experiments WHERE experiment_date >= '2022-01-01' AND experiment_date <= '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM experimental_conditions WHERE temperature > 100 AND pressure < 50 ORDER BY condition_id DESC;
SELECT team_id, researcher_name, institution FROM research_team WHERE email LIKE '%@example.com';
SELECT * FROM experiment_data;
SELECT id, biofuel_type, conversion_efficiency FROM experiment_data;
SELECT researcher_name, research_area FROM research_team;
SELECT * FROM experimental_setup ORDER BY setup_id DESC;
SELECT experiment_date, biofuel_type FROM experiment_data WHERE conversion_efficiency > 0.5;
SELECT * FROM experiment_data;
SELECT research_area, researcher_name FROM research_team ORDER BY researcher_name DESC;
SELECT setup_id, equipment_used, setup_description FROM experimental_setup WHERE setup_id BETWEEN 2 AND 5;
SELECT experiment_id, analysis_result FROM results_analysis WHERE analysis_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT biofuel_type, conversion_efficiency FROM experiment_data INNER JOIN results_analysis ON experiment_data.id = results_analysis.experiment_id;
SELECT * FROM Biofuel_Research_Experiments;
SELECT experiment_id, experiment_date, biofuel_type FROM Biofuel_Research_Experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC;
SELECT technique_name, description FROM Research_Techniques WHERE technique_name ILIKE '%biofuel%';
SELECT researcher_name, affiliation FROM Researchers ORDER BY researcher_name ASC;
SELECT publication_title, publication_date FROM Research_Publications WHERE publication_date BETWEEN '2020-01-01' AND '2020-12-31';
SELECT * FROM Biofuel_Research_Experiments ORDER BY experiment_date DESC, efficiency ASC
SELECT experiment_id, biofuel_type, conversion_technique, efficiency FROM Biofuel_Research_Experiments WHERE efficiency > 0.8
SELECT technique_name, description FROM Research_Techniques WHERE technique_id IN (SELECT technique_id FROM Experiment_Results WHERE result_value > 0.5)
SELECT biofuel_type, conversion_technique, AVG(efficiency) AS average_efficiency FROM Biofuel_Research_Experiments GROUP BY biofuel_type, conversion_technique

SELECT r.researcher_name, r.affiliation, p.publication_title, p.publication_date FROM Researchers r INNER JOIN Research_Publications p ON r.researcher_id = p.researcher_id ORDER BY p.publication_date DESC
